                  <msItem>
                     <p> BATTLE or DE BELLO (Abbey of). <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename>, the
                  abbot</persName>, and <orgName key="org_102010">convent of Battle</orgName> notify that
                  <persName>
                           <forename>Thomas</forename>, bp. of <placeName key="place_101090" role="bishop" type="diocese">Norwich</placeName>
                        </persName>, has
                  granted and confirmed to the said abbey the church of <placeName role="church" key="place_102083">Ixning</placeName> 
                  in his diocese, to be appropriated to the use of the abbey
                  after the death of <persName>
                           <forename>George</forename>
                           <surname>Vercell<supplied>engio</supplied>
                           </surname>, rector</persName>, and
                        <persName>
                           <forename>Wido</forename>, vicar of the said church</persName>,
                  saving to the vicar 25 marks. Dated at <placeName role="date" key="place_102024">Battle</placeName>,
                     <origDate when="1229">1229</origDate>, 5 Ides November. 
                  .</p>
                  </msItem>
